name: Proud OBJKT (2021)
description: All proceeds will be donated to The Trevor Project on July 1, 2021. Unsold editions burned. All secondary proceeds (25%) will be donated to The Trevor Project on an interim basis thereafter. Receipts shared on Twitter (@JYD_0001). The Trevor Project provides crisis intervention and suicide prevention services to lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender and questioning (LGBTQ) young people under the age of 25 - www.thetrevorproject.org
